Package: flare
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, flare-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: single-player 2D action role-playing game
 This fantasy dungeon crawl game is a proof of concept implementation of the
 Free Libre Action Roleplaying Engine (FLARE). FLARE a simple
 isometric-perspective action role-play game engine in the basic style of
 Diablo.
 .
 This package contains the binaries.

Package: flare-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: flare (= ${source:Version})
Description: single-player 2D action role-playing game
 This fantasy dungeon crawl game is a proof of concept implementation of the
 Free Libre Action Roleplaying Engine (FLARE). FLARE a simple
 isometric-perspective action role-play game engine in the basic style of
 Diablo.
 .
 This package contains the data.
